! mindmap elixir

[[mind-elixir|https://github.com/SSShooter/mind-elixir-core]] engine adapter for [[rimir/mindmap|$:/plugins/rimir/mindmap]]. Registers as a `module-type: mindmapengine` so any `<$mindmap>` widget can render via mind-elixir.

!! Key features

* ''Drop-in adapter'' — install alongside `rimir/mindmap`, select `MindElixir` as the default engine
* ''Tree-native rendering'' — radial layout, expand/collapse, focus, drag with mind-elixir's defaults
* ''Round-trip safe'' — unknown-namespace attrs (`mx:*`, `kn:*`, etc.) survive engine swaps
* ''Bundled library'' — mind-elixir UMD + CSS shipped inside the plugin; no CDN or build step

!! Prerequisites

* `$:/plugins/rimir/mindmap`
* TiddlyWiki 5.3.0+

!! Quick start

# Install both `rimir/mindmap` and this plugin.
# Set `$:/config/rimir/mindmap/default-engine` to `MindElixir` (or leave empty — it's the only engine, the widget picks it up automatically).
# Render any view: `<$mindmap view="MyView"/>`.

!! Bundled version

mind-elixir v5.11.0 (MIT-licensed). See `changelog` for upgrades.
